g_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":6183,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/10\/greet-peace-do-not-know\/","url_meta":{"origin":2946,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Greet strangers with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr\u00a0reported: A man asked the Prophet, \u201cWhich Islam is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThat you feed the hungry and you greet with peace those you know and those you do not know.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 28, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 39 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9897,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/22\/ali-ibn-abi-talib-harun-musa\/","url_meta":{"origin":2946,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Prophets: Ali is to Muhammad as Aaron to Moses","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, set out to Tabuk and he left Ali behind. Ali said, \"You leave me behind with the women and children?\" The Prophet said, \"Are you not pleased in the same position for me as Aaron\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6589,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/jihad-killing-women-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":2946,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: The Prophet condemns killing women and children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: A woman was found killed in one of the battles of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, so the Prophet condemned the killing of women and children. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3014, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1744 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8202,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/prophet-pardon-jewish-woman\/","url_meta":{"origin":2946,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Pardon: The Prophet forgives woman who poisoned him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A Jewish woman came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, with a poisoned sheep, and he ate from it. She was brought to him and he asked her about it. She said, \"I want to kill you.\" The Prophet said, \"Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/gabriel-greet-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":2946,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jibreel: Angel Gabriel greets you with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and b